# Animation homework problem #1
frames 1 50
screen -3 -2 3 2
pixels 600 400
vary middle-sphere 0 180 1 50
vary left-box 0 360 1 50
vary right-box 0 360 1 50
save origin
rotate-x middle-sphere
sphere 1 10 1 1 1 30 0 0 0 0 0
restore origin
move 2 0 0
rotate-x right-box
cube .5 2 .5 0 right-box  0 0 0 0
restore origin
move -2 0 0
rotate-y left-box
cube .5 2 .5 30 0 0 0 0 0
render-perspective-cyclops 0 0 10
--files ex1_ 0 0 10
end
